{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "38e4b116-b4d1-4ff7-a7e3-84bc06b1c6fe",
    "name": "TerkOffice 04: Caught Red-handed",
    "storyEventId": "80a03a74-a297-4969-ad69-af9bb3d3538a",
    "sceneId": "60cb5886-83dd-4e8f-9953-a9eafd43c179",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "a148e9b3-acfa-476d-bb80-711e7781f9b0",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.incrementTime",
                    "id": "a0b90fc8-70fa-45e2-930a-9dfc63ddde52",
                    "days": 0,
                    "hours": 0,
                    "minutes": "20"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                    "id": "b14d3b77-ca0d-4b51-a359-7c6cef101dce",
                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                    "propId": "613efa0f-b42d-4604-b632-3df5b8af9db3",
                    "target": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "791583fe-1446-4a37-b3a6-89da337e758c",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "You are an absolute idiot!",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "3",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "879e2a72-9948-4e3b-b298-d565b7e51748",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "How could you be so stupid as to get caught breaking into a fellow student's room? Do you want to get kicked out of school?",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "e29e0f0a-99a8-437c-b052-fda65c55bad5",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "90efe2cc-fa4f-4cc2-aede-e4f3b15333ac",
                            "text": "Tell the Truth",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "f9ae4ec6-562c-4740-a849-b7968aa2b90b",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "40",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "319d14fe-ce90-41d8-ac73-3ad28b19b90c",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "It was a set-up. I was trying to recover something that Sosi stole from my friend.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ad8a3529-527d-45f5-9e12-6ba3f74f7062",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You expect me to believe you were trying to be a hero? Right.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b2ca9f9c-3355-4a68-9759-1be6ec403be6",
                            "text": "Talk Your Way Out of It ",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "679ff24a-09f8-4efc-9918-814bc22fb78b",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "40",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "59479bea-d1b1-42bb-b165-4b24f9904de2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I just happened to notice the door open on their dorm room and I went inside to see if Joel was around.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "bf160e1e-a87e-4e2c-a39f-77145174519d",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "And while you were in the empty room, you just thought you'd pick up a few things they wouldn't miss right away, is that it?",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "d225ddb0-30ce-405e-ac55-f054f0299868",
                            "text": "Answer Snarkily",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "23de5d29-ef9a-44c1-90fd-1a223f8f0bfc",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "40",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "23356f15-90d1-474b-91e7-94947bb193c7",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "Would you believe that it's Caesari's birthday today and I was giving him a surprise party?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "bec48680-3e9f-450c-9753-124f0c7a2593",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Don't be impertinent! You should be kicked out of school and thrown in jail to rot!",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e051d7f0-4707-4750-ab82-a8cb992f665f",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "The only reason why you aren't walking out the front gates right now is because your Patron still thinks that you can bring down Gerhard. ",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1cb813d0-5fe7-437c-810e-448aef0c2f12",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "So tell me, what have you learned so far... Do you have anything that will incriminate Master von Urwald?",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "bf039703-85cf-445d-ae7c-d8bbf9e18ca8",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "94ebd750-2eac-442f-b57b-afd5b04a2495",
                            "text": "Tell the Truth",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "8f944149-5521-4da2-8c28-d1af771b4863",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "40",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ffbd8e1c-6594-4aa9-bffa-5835ef0e6f22",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I have to get into Gerhard's office to find incriminating evidence, but the door is trapped. \nI'm trying to build up my skills with lock picks enough so that I can safely open the door.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "133985ba-ba5f-4e86-881e-abc8ea255085",
                            "text": "Bluff ",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "a44e8b6c-fee1-48ce-9fb5-a4eb79335189",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "40",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "108bc497-6e81-4025-9f3e-22945ed21d7f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I listened in on a conversation between Gerhard talking to Sosi about the black market Gerhard runs out of his office. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "088307d0-b0d8-441a-97b5-a182f4289321",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "Give me a week to sweet-talk the Master Rogue, and I'll be able to prove that Gerhard is just another Thief out to cheat the school.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5acba84b-8c78-48e4-8ba3-11b7475dbadd",
                            "text": "Answer Snarkily",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "f451c89d-b259-4cd4-bba1-4d75a54abb89",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "40",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "99650ffd-cdb2-4959-948e-0293654c8e21",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I learned that Blowhard has a very low opinion about people who encourage other people to do criminal acts... And that he knows something sinister about the local Chief Thief...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2349e669-4cdd-42a1-86bd-a84c22a9fd93",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Enough! I've had more than enough of your insolence.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "04f09174-a24b-48fe-97ea-b8f8edac4212",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "I'll let you off this one time for now, but you'd better come up with a way to get rid of Gerhard soon. Your Patron is losing patience with you.\nEither Gerhard goes - or you go.",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b7943555-4afb-4b6d-82a6-49f92f0ceca8",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Now get out of here - and don't get caught again!",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "bd12e5f4-88d4-4fbc-a6bc-669854a3cbb2",
                    "name": "Break-in Blues",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "Okay, so the second time I try to break into someplace, I got caught... Maybe there's a lesson here? Nah.\n\nJoel set me up to get caught by Sosi and Terk. Why am I not surprised? The only good news is that Terk is too afraid of my Patron to kick me out of the school... so far.\n\nTerk really, really wants me to get rid of Gerhard. That's easier said than done. Besides, if I had my druthers of who I'd like to see go - Gerhard or Terk? - Hmmm... I wonder."
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeScene",
                    "sceneId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
                    "spawnId": "2e1c2cd6-e8d8-4d69-8c37-68f7b246bb96",
                    "fadeTime": 2
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}